{"tid":1510344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣]中共眼中 -- 黃絲,藍絲,中立都沒有分別","createTime":"2019-08-27T06:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T15:33:26.000Z","uid":119715,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3848e3c239677ed60efe653fcc72a591cf688a6a","tid":1510344,"uid":119715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:56:35.000Z","msg":"無論你係黃絲,藍絲,中立,<br />\n支持警察還是支持示威者,<br />\n有錢佬還是基層,<br />\n<br />\n事件發展到今時今日, 在中共眼中,我們沒有分別, 我們都是港英餘孽<br />\n<br />\n大家都清楚中共的手段, 中共要開始清算,清洗的話,<br />\n不會只對付黃絲, 一定一視同人, 無一幸免<br />\n<br />\n事情已返唔到轉頭, <br />\n藍絲,中立者, 甚至警察<br />\n你們已經被迫上車了<br />\n不可能置身事外<br />\n<br />\n你們的選擇有兩個,<br />\n1. 繼續不支持這個運動, 然後兩三年後, 和你們最憎的黃絲住進同一個集中營<br />\n2. 一起反坑暴政<br />\n<br />\n是的, 你們已被強姦, 被夾上船了! <br />\n來,一起下地獄吧!"},{"pid":"46be477b11989c15d9440e6a2cc42c3aaa416f6b","tid":1510344,"uid":119715,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:56:46.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"f18f6d19eafa4889300e252baebd2ecfaead0732","tid":1510344,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bizUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=fb1a4c5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bizUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=921a19f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bizUBvjVF43IiJLn